CVE-2026-46378

# --- Miscellaneous transitive dependency CVEs ---
# All entries below are CVEs trivy fingerprints inside a tool's bundled
# JS/Python/Go modules. The repeated rationale (linters run as offline
# static scanners; inputs come from the workspace; no network services
# are exposed) is summarised at the top of the file. Per-CVE notes are
# kept where they identify which dependency is affected so renovate can
# drop the entry once the upstream linter is bumped.

