CVE-2026-54513

# --- betterleaks (secret scanner) ---
# CVEs in the prebuilt ghcr.io/betterleaks/betterleaks image. betterleaks
# is a secret scanner that MegaLinter runs as a short-lived CLI against
# local workspace files (`betterleaks dir .` / `betterleaks git .`).
# golang.org/x/crypto/ssh SSH client/server DoS and revocation-bypass
# CVEs: betterleaks never opens SSH connections nor acts as an SSH
# server in MegaLinter's usage. The stdlib x509 VerifyHostname CVE only
# matters for TLS verification of attacker-controlled certs, which the
# default `dir`/`git` scan does not perform (no --validation HTTP calls).
# All are fixed upstream; remove once betterleaks ships a rebuild with
# golang.org/x/crypto >= 0.52.0 and Go >= 1.25.11.
